                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in the Netherlands</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_VDH1" type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Van Dyke</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-04-14">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 14, 1915</hi>.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>142. British Embassy notifies Department tobacco, cocoa, and coffee destined to
                    Holland must be consigned to Overseas Trust. Has Overseas Trust now authority to
                    receive consignments non-contraband goods?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_BWJ1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
